---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="韭菜圈 | A 股条件单工具箱">
  <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 py-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:py-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-leaf">A 股 ETF/股票条件单辅助工具</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-6xl">把盘前计划变成可执行的条件单。</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-stone-700">
        韭菜圈先从一个高频工具开始：读取股票/ETF 行情快照，计算次日低吸价、高抛价和观察价，帮助你减少临盘情绪化操作。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/tools/condition-order" class="rounded-md bg-leaf px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-800">打开计算器</a>
        <a href="/strategies/condition-order" class="rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-5 py-3 font-semibold hover:border-leaf">查看策略说明</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between">
        <p class="font-semibold">Sprint 1 交付面板</p>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-leaf/15 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-leaf">工具已上线</span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-3">
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">核心工具</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xl font-bold">ETF/股票次日条件单计算器</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">数据形态</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xl font-bold">盘中定时快照 + 手动兜底</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-md border border-line p-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">下一功能</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xl font-bold">回测功能即将上线</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-white/55">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-4 px-4 py-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">自动行情</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-stone-700">后台脚本参考既有 stock/ETF 行情脚本，定时生成前端可读取的数据文件。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">纪律交易</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-stone-700">输出可复制的条件单文案，让交易计划在开盘前完成。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">稳步变现</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-stone-700">先验证复用和早鸟会员，再决定小程序、广告和完整会员系统。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
